(years ago, in the aftermath of Bush v Gore, I got involved in a bunch of ugly tech policy) Tj
T*
(fights over voting machines. The hanging chad debacle in Florida prompted Congress to) Tj
T*
(appropriate funds for states to purchase new touchscreen voting machines based on a robust,) Tj
T*
(open standard. The problem was, those machines didn't exist. The voting machine industry in) Tj
T*
(those days was already very consolidated \(it's far more consolidated today\). They went shopping) Tj
T*
(for a standards body that would publish a spec for a "standard" voting machine that cou...) Tj
